optional_parameters.name: imageUrl
optional_parameters.description: Please choose one of the parameters, either "imageFile" or "inputimage". If you choose "imageUrl", please enter a valid URL starting with "http(s)://" or a base64 string. For example, you can enter "http://www.olavsplates.com/foto_e/e_1657dtp.jpg" as an inputurl or "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGg...." as a base64 string for the inputimage parameter.
